urls.title: Data Reveals Increased Miscarriages After COVID Vaccination In First Trimester
urls.description: Not that long ago, our medical professionals would have never, ever vaccinated a woman during pregnancy. But today, injections during pregnancy are becoming routine, despite limited safety data. For many women, it may seem like it’s no big deal to get a TDaP or a Flu shot during pregnancy, but it may surprise you to learn that the recommendations for these injections during pregnancy came as recently as 2013, and 2004, respectively. Vaccines during pregnancy are still a very new thing. We should ALL be
